FixtureType.Description: ArcPod 15Q is a compact exterior wash fixture, featuring high-intensity light despite its small size. The unit is equipped with 15x10W RGBW / FC LEDs, delivering an exceptional output over than 5'900 lumens and a wide gamut of colours and whites. The slim sizing, as well as the wide range of available optics, makes the ArcPod 15Q an incredibly flexible architectural fixture to complement the bigger versions in large outdoor installs as accent light or for smaller-sized projects.
